  const opts = [
    `Yo${n}! Marcus here. I see you're coming in as a${lvl==='beginner'?' beginner — solid move starting early':lvl==='advanced'?' advanced lifter — let's see what you've got':' intermediate lifter'}, goal is ${gDesc}. That's what I'm built for.\n\nBefore I build anything for you, I need more context. Tell me — what does your current training look like? How many days a week, what split if any, and what's your biggest weak point right now?`,
